  "description": "A vibrant, clear-sky shot featuring four brown pelicans in flight. They are captured mid-air, wings outstretched, against a brilliant blue background. The pelicans exhibit varying positions, suggesting a dynamic flock movement. Their plumage shows gradients of brown and white, with darker wingtips. The lighting is bright and even, highlighting the texture of the feathers and the sleek bodies of the birds. There is a sense of natural freedom and aerial grace.",
